{
  "stem": "13198.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I used to say, you know, here's a spoonful for you, and a spoonful for you, and a spoonful till the mug was empty.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, because I was thin, always been thin, I had a small tummy and I didn't need to fill it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I-- I never had all the terrible pains that other people had.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Real stomach aches they used to have, because there's nothing in their tummies.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had hunger pains, but not so violent that I-- you know, I just had to put up with it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I did, but never as bad as other people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was always very grateful that I had such a tiny tummy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It didn't have to be filled all the time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Drank a lot of water, of course, which was good, if the water's clean.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They all had-- I think they must have caught it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had-- what's this thing that children always have?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Chickenpox and the other pox, the bad one, Smallpox.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had-- I caught smallpox.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was very ill with smallpox.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I thought I'd never survive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were doctors that came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can't even remember if there was anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't think they could do much, really.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You just had to rest.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So all you-- rest didn't cost anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were stuck up on the three tier thing on the top waiting to get better.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Wood.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Hard wood with a blanket, not much comfort.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was supposed to be the place where you didn't get sent on to be gassed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a-- so you know, you were grateful that you were there.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
